Components developed by CELYA:
-------------------------------

- Electron wrapper implementation for desktop deployment
- Custom window management and system tray integration
- Incoming call notification system with custom UI
- Single instance lock mechanism
- Enhanced media permissions handling
- Custom branding and packaging configuration
- Linux-specific optimizations and build configurations

